>> title: Thai Green Curry Bowl
>> cuisine: Thai
>> tags: bowl, quick-assembly, vegan, gluten-free, soy-free
>> servings: 1

-- Assembly time: 3 minutes

Scoop @../components/grains/jasmine-rice{1%cup} into #bowl{} as base.

Heat @../components/proteins/thai-green-curry{1.5%cups} and ladle over rice.

Garnish with @fresh Thai basil{4-5%leaves} and @lime{1}(wedge).

-- Warming, aromatic curry over fragrant rice
